snippet.title: EVERMOON: IN-GAME FEATURES (Alpha Ver.)
snippet.description:
When thinking of enjoyable #MOBA game, we think of Evermoon unique In-game Features 😉👾🔥

👥 CUSTOM PROFILE in your style
🏆 Push your rank to be on LEADERBOARD
💬 CHAT FEATURES to talk with your allies

Any other features are you looking for? Let us know in the comment👀👇
